                <h1>ISLE OF DOGS</h1>
                <h2>comedy | animation | adventure</h2>
                <p>When, by executive decree, all the canine pets 
                    of Megasaki City are exiled to a vast 
                    garbage-dump called Trash Island, 12-year-old 
                    Atari sets off alone in a miniature Junior-Turbo 
                    Prop and flies across the river in search of his 
                    bodyguard-dog, Spots. There, with the 
                    assistance of a pack of newly-found mongrel 
                    friends, he begins an epic journey that will 
                    decide the fate and future of the entire Prefecture.</p>
